  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study retreatment in patients who failed prior treatment with interferon alpha (pegylated
      or non-pegylated) with or without ribavirin in a real-life setting in an
      observational/noninterventional study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is an observational/non interventional study to collect data on the patient
      characteristics of those seeking retreatment as well as safety and efficacy information
      during the first 12 weeks of retreatment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
